flowchart TD
    A([API request with key]) --> B{Key present in header?}
    B -- No --> C([401 - API key required])
    B -- Yes --> D[Hash incoming API key with SHA-256]
    D --> E[Look up hash in database]
    E --> F{Key found?}
    F -- No --> G([401 - invalid API key])
    F -- Yes --> H{Key active and not expired?}
    H -- No --> I([401 - key revoked or expired])
    H -- Yes --> J[Load associated account and permissions]
    J --> K{Rate limit exceeded?}
    K -- Yes --> L([429 - rate limit exceeded])
    K -- No --> M{Key has required scope?}
    M -- No --> N([403 - insufficient permissions])
    M -- Yes --> O[Log usage event]
    O --> P([Process request and return response])
